<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT22">
<l>aḻakiyāṉ tāṉē yariyuruvaṉ tāṉē</l>
<l>paḻakiyāṉ tāḷē paṇimiṉ kuḻaviyāyt</l>
<l>tāṉē ḻulakukkun taṉmaikkun taṉmaiyaṉē</l>
<l>mīṉā yuyiraḷikkum vittu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The Essence of the seven worlds [and their] attributes,</l>
<l>the [First] Cause, who, as a child, as a fish, protects the souls,</l>
<l>is the Beautiful One; He is the One with a lion form.</l>
<l>Humble [yourselves] at the feet of the Intimate [Lord]!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
